reviewText: Great service.  Grand babies enjoying the movie!
Our child ADORES Miss Patty Cake!  We are so thankful for the wide selection of DVD's and CD's offered!  I don't know what her trick is, but she knows how to entertain little ones.
My Granddaughters enjoy watching this everyday, mostly singing, they don't want to hear Miss Pattycake talk.  Wish they hadn't discontinued production.
